Okay, let's create a basic portfolio structure. This will involve several new components and a global stylesheet.

I'll provide:1.  **`src/index.css`**: A global stylesheet for basic resets and body styles.
2.  **`src/App.jsx`**: The main application file that will assemble all the portfolio sections.3.  **`src/components/Hero.jsx` & `src/components/Hero.module.css`**: An updated Hero section for a portfolio.
4.  **`src/components/About.jsx` &`src/components/About.module.css`**: An "About Me" section.
5.  **`src/components/Skills.jsx` & `src/components/Skills.module.css`**: A sectionto list your skills.
6.  **`src/components/Projects.jsx` & `src/components/Projects.module.css`**: A section to showcase your projects.
7.  **`src/components/Contact.jsx` & `src/components/Contact.module.css`**: A contact form/information section.

